g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f285dac83c018623411e802265f291021ba7db","tid":435284,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁熱都話凍"},{"pid":"60cb060a5363b735539eb748cdf218f2ddb48009","tid":435284,"uid":68203,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:56:03.000Z","msg":"反暖化撚永遠只係識掩耳盜鈴式地用廢老非黑即白既邏輯去反駁<br />\n但永遠拎唔到實際數據證明地球其實冇暖化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eee46f5b0cc541ec7b0cd815093bef9ae03c994","tid":435284,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>暖化撚夏天有冇開冷氣</blockquote><br />\n靜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇"},{"pid":"f7c05c1adc538b9d4783f9dba27e5cc34006e334","tid":435284,"uid":117647,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得氣候極端化呢個term係近年先興有人講<br />\n早幾年都仲係全球暖化<br />\n即係依加係天氣一熱就全球暖化<br />\n一凍就氣候極端化<br />\n環保撚講晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 忍唔撚住要出聲教你班細路仔<br />\n到底你地知唔知全球暖化既影響<br />\n全球暖化 加劇 溫室效應  令兩極冰塊溶化 <br />\n因為溶既係大量淡水 所以影響左原先正常既洋流 而海洋既溫度係會影響所有既氣候  <br />\n導致到極端天氣既出現 ，令本身熱既地方會好凍 ，本身凍既地方會好熱。<br />\n又或者係不斷咁出現颱風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ff107c61722e7884f91b3222323701dd43cee6","tid":435284,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我記得氣候極端化呢個term係近年先興有人講<br />\n早幾年都仲係全球暖化<br />\n即係依加係天氣一熱就全球暖化<br />\n一凍就氣候極端化<br />\n環保撚講晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><b